                </figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Recycled Plastics</h2>
                    <p>Recycling plastics requires less energy than producing new materials and relieves demand for fossil-fuel-based raw materials. It also saves landfill space and reduces environmental pollution.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/solutions/projects/27">View Details</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
